name: Md Jasim Uddin
massage: I have a Sony digital camera that can be used with or without a memory stick. After taking pictures they load onto my laptop, for better viewing, via a data cord from the camera to the laptop, like a thumb drive or by moving the memory stick from the camera to the laptop.
